text: Farmington is an unincorporated community in Davie County, North Carolina. Located at the intersection NC 801 and Farmington Road (SR 1410), the area is a predominantly farming community. Located nearby is the Farmington Dragway. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Davie County, North Carolina Category:Unincorporated communities in North Carolina
title: Farmington, North Carolina
